<div >
    <ul class ="paw">
        <div class='FAQ'>
            <li>
                <button class='question'>How does it work?</button>
                <div class='answer'> 
                    <p>To access to this service you should do the following steps:
                            <ul>- Create an account </ul>
                            <ul>- Regist your pet(s)</ul>
                            <ul>- Make a request for a petsitter</ul>
                </div>
            </p>
            </li>
        </div>

        <div class='FAQ'>
        <li>
            <button class='question'>What type of pets do you take care of?</button>
            <p class='answer'>You can post any request you want, but it will depend on the availability and experience of the Petsitters.</p>
        </li>
        </div>

        <div class='FAQ'>
        <li>
            <button class='question'>Can I choose the Petsitter that I want to hire?</button>
            <p class='answer'>Absolutely yes! But it will depend on them availability.</p>
        </li>
        </div>

        <div class='FAQ'>
        <li >
            <button class='question'>How does the payment process work?</button>
            <p class='answer'>Pre-payment of 50% of the service price via MB way or bank transfer.</p>
        </li>
        </div>

        <div class='FAQ'>
        <li>
            <button class='question'>Are the petsitters qualified?</button>
            <p class='answer'>Yes! They will do their best to take care of your pet supplying all their needs.</p>
        </li>
        </div>

        <div class='FAQ'>
        <li>
            <button class='question'>Can I meet the Petsitter before hiring?</button>
            <p class='answer'>Yes. We encourage you to meet each other previously and introduce the animals. When you contact the petsitter you can schedule a visit or previous meeting.</p>
        </li>
        </div>

        <div class='FAQ'>
        <li>
            <button class='question'>I choosed the Petsitter but I didn't get the contact.</button>
            <p class='answer'>You need to make the pre-payment first.</p>
        </li>
        </div>

        <div class='FAQ'>
        <li>
            <button class='question'>Do you have a table price?</button>
            <p class='answer'>No. The prices are established by each Petsitter, so the prices can be variable according to each petsitter. </p>
        </li>
        </div>

        <div class='FAQ'>
        <li>
            <button class='question'>Will I get refunded if I cancel the service?</button>
            <p class='answer'>Only if you cancel the service with 7 or more days in advance. In order to refund you, we emit a credit of 50% of the total amount pre-payed and you can use it in the next service.</p>
        </li>
        </div>

        <div class='FAQ'>
        <li>
            <button class='question'>Does the prices include the feeding?</button>
            <p class='answer'>No. The food and all the materials needed to the maintenance of the animals should be provided by the owner.</p>
        </li>
        </div>

    </ul>
</div>


<script>
    let collapsible = document.getElementsByClassName("question");
    let i;

    for (i = 0; i < collapsible.length; i++) {
    collapsible[i].addEventListener("click", function() {
        this.classList.toggle("active");
        let answer = this.nextElementSibling;
        if (answer.style.display === "block") {
        answer.style.display = "none";
        } else {
        answer.style.display = "block";
        }
    });
    }
</script>